review_blob: Beer pours nice and black. Let it sit for a few minutes until the chill is out. Subtle sweetness and vanilla with a little bitterness at the end.

Aroma was amazing, pour was dark..black. First taste was pleasing, strong chocolate and coffee flavors. It was pretty cold but when it warmed up there was a little bitterness at the end, which I wasnt a fan of.  Overall kt was a good beer and I would drink it again but not the first one I grab.
beer_name: Left Hand Wake Up Dead Imperial Stout - Barrel-Aged

review_blob: Nice aroma out of the bottle, good taste with little to no after taste. Dark on color. Flavors are subtle.
beer_name: Brau Brothers Moo Joos Oatmeal Milk Stout

review_blob: Drank out the bottle, smooth taste with subtle notes of vanilla and bourbon. Little to no after taste.
